{"tid":1183403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同熱愛這片土地 大家刻骨銘記","createTime":"2019-06-03T01:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T03:04:37.000Z","uid":58766,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71b0ab0fbfa9cfb77e33f92b35ee73a475b0e631","tid":1183403,"uid":58766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"係得呢個地方出世 就預左係呢個地方度死<br />\n有人會睇到黃金片地 呢度係一塊福地<br />\n有人會睇到唔一樣 樣樣野一敗塗地<br />\n有人會識得設身處地 有人會選擇逃避<br />\n有人會認為呢個係環境同人既問題<br />\n呢度既文化一潭死水點會居安思危<br />\n七百萬隻螞蟻 唔容易走埋一齊<br />\n向住同一個方向睇 一定會搵到大前題<br />\n係同一種人 點解要將人睇低<br />\n係同一種人 可以學埋同一種語文<br />\n講第二種語文唔表示你係第二種人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩時間都啱聽"},{"pid":"07a72d641fd05e0c05a093b929c34b8b34fe639c","tid":1183403,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"因為100毛先識呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e00f212ad516bb2b49857429b86eb06d5c6bfc","tid":1183403,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd950530318151fb4e8e826229e4961a8b8a5a7c","tid":1183403,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xCTJPWXDBqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxCTJPWXDBqY&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=74642e7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xCTJPWXDBqY</a>"},{"pid":"8c962c74c36838aa635599673792a36fe8351c7c","tid":1183403,"uid":191633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07a72d641fd05e0c05a093b929c34b8b34fe639c","tid":1183403,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"因為100毛先識呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" clas